# Data Layer

This folder contains the dataset used in the iFood Marketing Analytics project.

## Dataset

Expected file:

```text
ifood_marketing.csv
```

## Important Note

This project uses a public/educational marketing dataset and should not be interpreted as official iFood data.

The dataset is used only for portfolio, learning and demonstration purposes.

## Main Fields

Examples of fields used in the analysis:

- Customer ID / Index
- Income
- Age
- Recency
- Customer days
- Product spending columns
- Purchase channel columns
- Campaign acceptance columns
- Education
- Marital status
- Response

## Data Preparation

The Python and SQL layers use this dataset to generate:

- Treated analytical base
- Business KPIs
- Customer segmentation
- Campaign response prediction
- Executive business insights

## Privacy

No real personal identifiable information is used in this project.
